        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/missions/submissions/{{submission_id}}/approve",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["v1", "missions", "submissions", "{{submission_id}}", "approve"]
        },
        "description": "Admin approves the submission.\n\n**🎯 THIS IS WHERE THE MAGIC HAPPENS! 🎯**\n\n**Workflow:**\n1. Update submission status → approved\n2. Update assignment status → completed\n3. Create mission_reward_grant record\n4. **EMIT MISSION_REWARD_GRANTED event to outbox** ⭐\n\n**Outbox Pattern Flow:**\n```\nMissions Plugin:\n  └─ Insert into outbox table\n     └─ event_name: MISSION_REWARD_GRANTED\n     └─ payload: {reward_grant_id, assignment_id, user_id}\n\nOutbox Processor (async):\n  └─ Poll outbox table\n  └─ Find unprocessed events\n  └─ Deliver to wallet consumer\n  └─ Mark event as processed\n\nWallet Consumer:\n  └─ Receive MISSION_REWARD_GRANTED event\n  └─ Read mission_reward_grant table\n  └─ Auto-create account if needed\n  └─ Auto-create wallet if needed\n  └─ Create double-entry ledger transaction\n  └─ Credit 50 COIN to user wallet\n  └─ Update wallet_balance_snapshot\n  └─ Link back to mission_reward_grant\n  └─ Emit WALLET_CREDITED event\n```\n\n**API:** POST /v1/missions/submissions/{id}/approve\n**Spec:** specs/mission/missions.pillar.v2.yml lines 349-456\n\n**Events Emitted:**\n- MISSION_SUBMISSION_APPROVED\n- MISSION_COMPLETED\n- MISSION_REWARD_GRANTED ⭐ (triggers wallet credit)"
      },
      "response": []
    },
